{"tid":2409814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲：或取消維多利亞州與中國的一帶一路協議 稱協議沒有任何好處","createTime":"2021-02-16T06:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T08:20:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d8265769af5cc609bd1f417b6fdbf479c462a6be","tid":2409814,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"莫里森：或取消維多利亞州與中國的一帶一路協議<br />\n<br />\n澳洲總理莫里森表示，維多利亞州與中國在2019年簽訂的一帶一路協議「沒有任何好處」，或在數星期內取消有關協議。澳洲財長弗萊登伯格亦表示，聯邦政府一直不同意簽訂有關協議，待適當時機政府就會作出決定。州長安德魯斯堅稱，一帶一路協議可為維多利亞州帶來更多就業、貿易和投資機會。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲去年12月通過《外交關係法》，地方政府必須在3月10日前，向聯邦政府報告與外國達成的所有協議，而聯邦政府可基於不利外交關係或與外交政策不一致，否決有關協議。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2379231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2379231&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=3101256c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2379231</a>"},{"pid":"19c6b0e1e4ac06c617407d8ed0c3056d8477cd5a","tid":2409814,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a40ddb06fd45869cae4bbe8fa11a4878dc6d6f","tid":2409814,"uid":338630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1e91bba9f30ebb9b61288f7f8857b071da9a3bc","tid":2409814,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:38:20.000Z","msg":"莫里森好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5d07373b6330b01d4a0084c8266904eef04c42","tid":2409814,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c1e91bba9f30ebb9b61288f7f8857b071da9a3bc","tid":2409814,"uid":158888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:38:2